{"tid":2332119,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"SEVENTEEN「隔離中」KBS硬叫去預錄　工作人員爆：不准他們戴口罩","createTime":"2020-12-19T10:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T07:58:09.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f636a1032bec83343a0abf7bc3e999fa8d9c732b","tid":2332119,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T10:55:32.000Z","msg":"南韓新冠肺炎疫情（COVID-19）持續升溫，電視台卻沒有要放棄年末活動的意思。KBS《歌謠大祝祭》18日舉行，由於舞台事前已經錄製完成，沒想到電視台仍要求演出歌手，冒著疫情風險到場只為了「走紅毯」，引起粉絲不滿。19日再爆出被取消演出的SEVENTEEN，其實也被叫去待機一整天。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5263/d5263717.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5263%2Fd5263717.jpg&h=37daa51f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲SEVENTEEN被KBS《歌謠大祝祭》強行召喚至現場。（圖／翻攝SEVENTEEN官方臉書）<br />\n<br />\n南韓疫情再攀高峰，不僅單日確診人數破千創新高，疫情也延燒至演藝圈。儘管多名偶像歌手和化妝師等相關工作人員陸續確診，電視台仍決定照常舉行年末活動。18日播出的KBS《歌謠大祝祭》就召集包括防彈少年團、TWICE、NCT、IZ*ONE等24組藝人，至於SEVENTEEN則因為正在自主隔離，最終取消演出。<br />\n<br />\n不過19日《Dispatch》以「KBS強行召喚偶像待機，新冠防疫只是作秀」為題，踢爆SEVENTEEN明明已經宣布全體檢測，並在結果出來前自行隔離，結果KBS卻以「沒有時間等待解禁」為由，強行要求SEVENTEEN參與彩排和預錄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5343/d5343100.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5343%2Fd5343100.jpg&h=c4e164c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲KBS要求參加《歌謠大祝祭》的偶像戴口罩走紅毯。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／KBS World）<br />\n<br />\n當時SEVENTEEN除了隊長S.COUPS，另外12名成員都已確定檢測結果為陰性。但KBS沒有等到全員檢測結果出爐，強行要求除了他們到現場彩排，並由舞者頂替S.COUPS的位置。彩排結束後，成員還做完妝髮待機了4個小時，最後因為S.COUPS檢測結果當天確定無法出爐，KBS才放人，讓經歷一整天混亂的SEVENTEEN回宿舍休息。<br />\n<br />\n遭受同樣待遇的，還有SM娛樂旗下的NCT，他們因為化妝師與確診者路線重疊，因此自主做了檢測，雖然一度宣布取消參與預錄，但「所幸」檢測結果即時出爐，也確定全員都是陰性，而在拿到結果後，就火速趕到電視台錄製。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5344/d5344658.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5344%2Fd5344658.jpg&h=b6e64888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲NCT一確定全員陰性就趕到電視台，走紅毯時也被要求戴上口罩。（圖／圖／翻攝自YouTube／KBS World）<br />\n<br />\n諷刺的是，同樣是KBS電視台，卻宣布為了防疫安全，即將舉辦的「演藝大賞」將採取「非面對面形式」頒獎，得獎者不需要到現場，而是會提前拍攝獲獎畫面，沒想到對於偶像歌手卻是兩種待遇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5343/d5343189.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5343%2Fd5343189.jpg&h=6076ddf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲相關工作人員踢爆，KBS不准參加《歌謠大祝祭》的偶像在待機室戴口罩。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／ KBS World）<br />\n<br />\n更讓粉絲擔心的是，有相關人員指出，KBS要求偶像歌手們在「會拍攝到畫面」的紅毯戴口罩現身，但藝人在待機室（後台）時，卻不能戴口罩。也讓相關工作人員感嘆：「偶像出席活動，包括隨行人員，一定都會超過10個人，這種情況很容易發生感染。藉口檢測被判定陰性，就認為不會發生問題，而強行舉辦活動是非常危險的。」"},{"pid":"ebfd2dc7febec683cd85e89c028e5b1ab9013bab","tid":2332119,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"痴線架唔好傳染到我啲bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4b1c53efa91c7d0967ef279d5ce983a6c9337d","tid":2332119,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ebfd2dc7febec683cd85e89c028e5b1ab9013bab","tid":2332119,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"痴線架唔好傳染到我啲bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T10:58:11.000Z","msg":"KPOP群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2957ceb0990ecdc48849b446914c7d0a6a85cc6","tid":2332119,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T12:01:34.000Z","msg":"真係cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713c9cf78c60344876282e6db11a16d3b6da3e62","tid":2332119,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2957ceb0990ecdc48849b446914c7d0a6a85cc6","tid":2332119,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T12:01:34.000Z","msg":"真係cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T12:02:30.000Z","msg":"爆吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa48414ac84ce62f7b26e753dc2324beae26c79","tid":2332119,"uid":18755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T07:58:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rx2iStX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRx2iStX.png&h=a4955bd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n抵死"}]}